Installation
=================
To install the "Video-Sites" extension follow these simple steps:

 1. Upload the extension using the Administration
 2. Install the "Video-Sites - Player" extension
 3. Activate the "YouTube" Plugin to display videos from YouTube and/or "Vimeo" for Vimeo videos


INTRODUCTION
=================
To add a YouTube video simply add [youtube]youtube-id[/youtube] to the pages content and replace
"youtube-id" with the YouTube Video ID. 

To add a Vimeo video add [vimeo]vimeo-id[/vimeo] to the pages content and replace
"vimeo-id" with the Vimeo Video ID. 

Please <a href="http://wiki.bigace.de/bigace:extensions:youtube" target="_blank">read the documentation</a> for more infos about using the Plugin.

CONFIGURATION
=================
This extension brings the new configuration package "video" with the following settings:
- player.class       the Video-Player css class
- player.width       the Video-Player width
- player.height      the Video-Player css class
- player.title       the Video-Player title

